        <mxCell id="legend" value="Request flow&#10;&#10;1 · Load the page (S3 / CloudFront)&#10;2 · Ask a question — POST /ask&#10;3 · API Gateway → Ask Lambda&#10;4 · Bedrock: question → SQL, then explain&#10;5 · Invoke the in-VPC query Lambda&#10;6 · Run the SQL on Aurora&#10;&#10;Read-only SELECT/WITH, guarded · credentials via&#10;VPC endpoint · Ask Lambda is outside the VPC ·&#10;seeder loads data on deploy · Aurora auto-pauses" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;strokeColor=#D6DBE0;fillColor=#FAFAFA;fontColor=#39485A;" parent="1" vertex="1">
